39
00:02:43,330 --> 00:02:45,580
- Here.
- I got it, I got it.

40
00:02:48,729 --> 00:02:50,689
Easy. Right there.

41
00:02:51,129 --> 00:02:54,250
All right, let your arms out.

42
00:02:57,129 --> 00:02:59,449
Okay. Sh.

43
00:03:01,330 --> 00:03:04,069
- What did I do?
