of the prophecy.

50
00:03:40,330 --> 00:03:42,719
Everyone and everything
will come for him.

51
00:03:43,330 --> 00:03:45,500
Which means we need a plan.

52
00:03:46,330 --> 00:03:49,169
Think I figured it out.

53
00:03:51,129 --> 00:03:52,599
He wet himself.

54
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:49,199
We could use your help.
When you finish--

55
00:04:49,250 --> 00:04:51,319
--changing the baby on my desk.

56
00:04:52,250 --> 00:04:53,899
Sorry, I needed the space.

57
00:04:54,050 --> 00:04:55,839
You nearly had sex
on my desk...

58
00:04:56,449 --> 00:04:59,430
...so I shouldn't be surprised
there's a baby on it.

59
00:05:00,050 --> 00:05:03,139
That was some guy
who switched bodies with me...

60
00:05:03,649 --> 00:05:07,060
