What? You can't be wet,
I just changed you.

76
00:06:01,850 --> 00:06:04,689
Are you hungry?
I got a bottle all ready for you.

77
00:06:04,850 --> 00:06:08,360
Where did I put his bottle?
I had his bottle ready for him.

78
00:06:11,449 --> 00:06:14,639
Okay. Here's your ba-ba.

79
00:06:15,649 --> 00:06:17,089
Take your ba-ba.

80
