I helped raise my cousin.

82
00:06:25,850 --> 00:06:27,430
I can handle it.

83
00:06:28,850 --> 00:06:31,100
We have to erase
everyone on the list.

84
00:06:31,250 --> 00:06:32,720
- I can do that.
- Fred?

85
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,279
What?

86
00:06:34,850 --> 00:06:38,990
