violent kind of way.

87
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:42,420
I'll just put that back.

88
00:06:43,250 --> 00:06:44,860
Come on, it's a nice ba-ba.

89
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:48,670
You wanna stop crying and take
your ba-ba, yes you do. Please?

90
00:06:50,290 --> 00:06:52,680
That was thrilling.
Not like I waited for you...

91
00:06:53,290 --> 00:06:56,449
