209
00:14:51,009 --> 00:14:54,629
The anxious one that's been
coming off you since he was born.

210
00:14:55,809 --> 00:14:57,250
He's connected to you.

211
00:14:57,610 --> 00:14:59,860
If you're wound tight,
how do you think he feels?

212
00:15:00,009 --> 00:15:03,340
He's not a day old, and he's got an
enemies list. Wouldn't you be edgy?

213
00:15:04,210 --> 00:15:06,809
Yeah. I'd also be in awe.

214
00:15:07,210 --> 00:15:08,750
Look at him.

215
00:15:13,210 --> 00:15:15,139
He's more than a mission, bro.

216
00:15:15,610 --> 00:15:17,009
Look at him.

217
