00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:55,809
Do you like that?

223
00:15:55,809 --> 00:15:58,440
No, obviously.
Okay, how about this one?

224
00:16:07,210 --> 00:16:08,610
Okay.

225
00:16:09,009 --> 00:16:11,539
I only got one more.

226
00:16:28,809 --> 00:16:33,620
That's my little guy.

227
00:16:34,809 --> 00:16:36,879
You like that, don't you?

228
00:16:47,049 --> 00:16:50,809
Lilah Morgan, clearance 0112773.

229
00:16:52,450 --> 00:16:54,549
There we are.
What can I do for you?

230
00:16:54,850 --> 00:16:57,450
I want everything the firm
has on Angel.

231
00:16:57,850 --> 00:17:01,039
His life history, unlife history,
intercept records...

232
00:17:02,049 --> 00:17:03,629
...victim lists, everything.

233
00:17:03,850 --> 00:17:07,750
I'm looking for someone he crossed
paths with 100 years ago or more.

234
00:17:08,650 --> 00:17:12,759
And make it fast. The boys upstairs
are at Defcon, like, 1000.

235
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:16,190
Sure thing, Miss Morgan.
Just a sec.

236
00:17:20,650 --> 00:17:21,910
Everything's in there?

237
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:25,400
Down to the baby that wasn't
supposed to be born.

238
00:17:26,049 --> 00:17:27,910
